
# Go to API Gateway in the AWS Console.

# Create a new API, select Rest 

# Then create a stage 

# Create a resource (enable CORS)

# Within that resource, create a method GET, enable Use Lambda Proxy Integration (enter the name of your function that been triggered)

# Click save and click deploy 

# The endpoint URL will like: https://(...).execute-api.ap-southeast-2.amazonaws.com/test/py-hello

# Then we can use Artillery for testing